<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0006936> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A process in which force is generated within muscle tissue, resulting in a change in muscle geometry. Force generation involves a chemo-mechanical energy conversion step that is carried out by the actin/myosin complex activity, which generates force through ATP hydrolysis." .
